Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.31,0:00:09.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tinju bom tanpa batas.\NMari lihat kapan kau akan tumbang.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.85,0:00:12.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.75,0:00:28.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.15,0:00:30.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,ini bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.31,0:00:33.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serangan selemah itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.45,0:00:39.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan ratusan kali pun,\Naku tak merasakan apa-apa!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.56,0:00:42.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.25,0:00:51.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.53,0:00:54.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hoodie All Might\Nedisi eksklusif Sky Egg?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, bergoyang lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini benar-benar cuma gempa?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.65,0:02:50.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ruang kontrol, ini Ingenium.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi di Sky Egg?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bos, tolong angkat teleponnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.91,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Hubungi pihak manajemen!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.91,0:02:58.74,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,- Bagaimana keadaan penonton?\N- Haruskah aku periksa keadaan di luar?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Halo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.53,0:03:17.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Listrik padam!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ponselku hilang sinyal.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.85,0:03:20.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.75,0:03:22.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, ponselku juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.85,0:03:35.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Denyut elektromagnetik menghentikan\Nkerja semua perangkat elektronik.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.31,0:03:41.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, tak boleh ada\Nyang mengganggu pertarungan Captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.45,0:03:47.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini peta tata letak Sky Egg.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat gempa atau mati listrik,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.50,0:03:52.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,lift akan mati\Ndan tangga darurat terbuka.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.95,0:03:58.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, saat ini, semua kunci elektronik\Nterkunci rapat otomatis.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.05,0:04:02.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Artinya... kita terjebak.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.31,0:04:04.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oleh seseorang...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Secara sengaja.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.26,0:04:11.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan sekadar\Nkecelakaan atau bencana.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.51,0:04:13.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Melainkan serangan dengan niat jahat...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, hei, maksudmu ini terorisme?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.78,0:04:18.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenanglah, Desutegoro.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.51,0:04:19.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau malah panik?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam keadaan darurat, pahlawan harus\Nmemberi rasa aman bagi warga.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Tsukauchi, bagaimana kondisi\NCaptain Celebrity?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.35,0:04:30.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak diketahui.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.45,0:04:36.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan berasumsi terburuk,\Nbahwa dia tak bisa bergerak saat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.21,0:04:39.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan atasi situasi ini\Ndengan pahlawan yang ada di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.91,0:04:42.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memeriksa kondisi di dalam dan luar,\Nmemastikan keselamatan penonton,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.56,0:04:46.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,menjalin komunikasi dengan pihak luar,\Nserta bersiap menghadapi musuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.80,0:04:51.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari bagi tugas sesuai\Nbidang keahlian Quirk masing-masing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita memegang tanggung jawab\Natas 50.000 nyawa di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak boleh ada satu pun korban.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.91,0:05:02.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari kita gabungkan kekuatan masing-masing\Nuntuk membuat sebuah jaring pengaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengerti, semuanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hal yang paling kubenci\Nadalah kerja tim!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.81,0:05:09.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, dengarkan aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.98,0:05:15.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Guncangan dan mati listrik sejak tadi\Ndisebabkan oleh gempa bumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah informasi yang kami terima!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong tetap di tempat\Nsampai situasi aman.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong tetap di tempat!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika ada yang merasa kurang sehat,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,silakan beri tahu kami!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.35,0:05:45.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lubang inspeksi di atas kubah\Nbisa dibuka secara manual.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tak bisa langsung turun\Nke bawah dari sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama, kita menuju lubang inspeksi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.37,0:05:59.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar mereka yang punya Quirk terbang keluar\Ndan menghubungi pihak luar.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.38,0:06:05.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika listrik gagal pulih,\Nkita panggil pesawat evakuasi...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bergoyang lagi...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.61,0:06:11.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di situasi begini,\Nkita sangat butuh kekuatan C.C...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.85,0:06:13.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bos!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ups, maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hampir tertidur barusan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.82,0:06:35.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pukulanmu senyaman angin sepoi-sepoi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.18,0:06:48.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau juga sudah\Nhampir mencapai batas, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.01,0:06:55.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selalu meledakkan tinjumu sendiri...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.31,0:06:58.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak mungkin kau bisa\Nberegenerasi tanpa batas, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.52,0:07:02.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan saling membuang waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga sedang di tengah pekerjaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.75,0:07:08.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Melawanmu\Nbukan bagian dari pekerjaanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.91,0:07:10.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini cuma fan service!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.31,0:07:20.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.98,0:07:33.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ini pria yang melindungi menara langit\Ndengan kedua tanganku sendiri!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.41,0:07:35.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,The Crawler Sky Egg!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nak, apa yang kau lakukan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.98,0:07:38.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat lari!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.01,0:07:43.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi Captain terus dipukuli!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.55,0:07:46.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak! Aku tak dipukuli!\NAku baik-baik saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan keras kepala begitu!\NMerepotkan sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.81,0:07:55.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kuserang tinju bomnya dari jauh\Ndan meledakkannya sebelum kena...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serangan langsung bisa dihindari!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tembakan beruntun pemungkas...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.85,0:08:07.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,The Crawler! KGDDDDD!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuatkan Gelora dan...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dor, dor, dor, dor, doooor!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Nak.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.85,0:08:21.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku baru sadar\Nsesuatu yang sangat penting!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.41,0:08:22.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya?! Apa itu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.01,0:08:24.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.45,0:08:27.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada dasarnya cuma mengulur waktu...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau lebih tepatnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.75,0:08:32.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini tak benar-benar\Nmenyelesaikan masalah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apalagi dia bisa beregenerasi!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.98,0:08:38.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perkelahian kacau juga tak apa-apa!\NKalau ledakannya semencolok ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,para pahlawan pasti segera datang!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.98,0:08:46.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau masih mengandalkan orang lain\Ndi saat seperti ini?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.01,0:08:48.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berusaha semaksimal mungkin,\Nlalu mengandalkan orang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.59,0:08:51.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu memang gayaku sejak dulu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.95,0:08:55.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh... itu sama sekali tidak terdengar keren.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.78,0:09:01.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi... sepertinya sekarang\Ncuma itu satu-satunya cara.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.55,0:09:04.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengandalkanmu, Nak!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siap!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.41,0:09:20.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dia arahkan tinjunya ke Captain...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.11,0:09:22.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menghentikannya dengan KGD!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.37,0:09:32.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan terus mengikuti gerakannya\Nsupaya bisa terus melindungi Captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu KGD lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.63,0:09:39.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kalau saat itu daya lekat\Ndi kakiku tak aktif...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan jatuh!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Nak, hati-hati!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, terima kasih...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.01,0:09:52.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau jatuh,\Npertahananku hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.98,0:09:57.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan kalau aku tumbang,\Npenopang kubah Sky Egg juga hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua karena kelalaianmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan memberiku tekanan lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nak, lakukan yang terbaik!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.25,0:10:18.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak dulu aku selalu populer.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.55,0:10:25.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat aku terbang, semua orang\Ntersenyum dan melambaikan tangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.65,0:10:30.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang dewasa maupun anak-anak...\Nterutama para gadis.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.25,0:10:59.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.25,0:11:03.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau memasang wajah murung di depanku,\Naku tidak bisa mengabaikannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.11,0:11:09.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan apa-apa...\Nwajahku memang dari awal begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.61,0:11:17.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah! Tapi aku tahu sebuah sihir\Nyang bisa mengubahnya jadi senyuman.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini dia!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.70,0:11:26.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya Chris lebih hebat\Ndaripada roller coaster!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.25,0:11:29.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau takut, peluk aku erat-erat\Ndan teriak "Kyaa!", ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.86,0:11:31.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.65,0:11:36.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu sebentar! Aku jatuh!\NAku akan segera menurunkanmu sekarang!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak suka yang seperti itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memaksakan roller coaster ke orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.11,0:11:46.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan senyum menyebalkanmu itu\Njuga bikin kesal.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.38,0:11:49.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru pertama kali\Nada yang bilang begitu padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.85,0:11:50.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.18,0:11:53.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada orang yang marah pada balon.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Balon?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.15,0:11:58.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlalu ceria, melayang-layang,\Ntapi kosong di dalam.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu aku?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.85,0:12:03.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kejam sekali kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.91,0:12:16.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hai, halo, aku balon.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, soal kemarin maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.35,0:12:22.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku cuma ingin membuatmu senang...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.75,0:12:25.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau masih marah?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kukira kau membenciku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.61,0:12:36.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu pertama kali bertemu,\Nkau menatapku tajam.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bukan...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.51,0:12:38.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.75,0:12:44.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku cuma berpikir... sepertinya akan\Nmenyenangkan kalau bisa terbang begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya! Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau roller coaster, tak usah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.41,0:12:52.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang suka begitu\Ncuma orang bodoh dan anak-anak.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke, kalau begitu kita pakai balon saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Balon?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.25,0:13:04.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terbang serendah ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita pasti terlihat sangat konyol.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.60,0:13:12.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau itu maumu,\Ntur balon akan segera dimulai!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.21,0:13:18.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak ingin dibenci siapa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terutama oleh para gadis.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan saat itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.15,0:13:29.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin aku juga berpikir untuk\Nmenjinakkan gadis keras kepala ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.98,0:13:32.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.21,0:13:42.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada akhirnya, justru aku...\Nyang dijinakkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah itu aku terus mengejarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.38,0:13:53.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin dia melihat ke arahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin membuatnya tersenyum.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.51,0:14:00.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Chris,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.15,0:14:04.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau benar-benar idiot yang menyebalkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.91,0:14:08.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi sebagian besar dunia dipenuhi\Norang-orang yang benar-benar sampah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.51,0:14:14.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dibandingkan mereka... kurasa\Nkau mungkin sedikit lebih baik...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kadang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.65,0:14:20.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu berarti... "iya"... 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.75,0:14:28.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Chris, hentikan! Aku akan marah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.34,0:14:33.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang, kalau takut, peluk aku erat-erat\Ndan teriak "Kyaa!", ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.71,0:14:36.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bodoh...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sangat bahagia waktu itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.81,0:14:47.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai sekarang kita akan selalu bersama.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.85,0:14:51.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa menjalani hidup tiap hari\Nsambil melihat senyummu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.21,0:14:55.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat itu... aku sungguh berpikir begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.71,0:15:06.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi pada akhirnya,\Nkau selalu marah padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.51,0:15:11.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah kenapa, pekerjaanku juga\Nmakin lama makin memburuk...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.97,0:15:15.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang-orang yang kuanggap teman dekat...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.58,0:15:19.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mencatut namaku untuk menipu orang\Ndan merampas uang mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan saat kupikir aku telah\Nmengalahkan penjahat...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.65,0:15:26.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku malah dituntut,\Ndan akhirnya aku yang dianggap bersalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana sebenarnya letak kesalahanku?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.16,0:15:33.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang... apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.95,0:15:38.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Urusan soal keluarga dan dunia,\Nsemuanya terasa sulit bagiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama apa pun kupikirkan,\Naku tak bisa memahaminya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, Captain...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau tersenyum?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.41,0:15:50.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ups, maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.22,0:15:53.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya teringat sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Musuhnya adalah penjahat bom\Nyang sangat berbahaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lima puluh ribu nyawa ada di pundakku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.81,0:16:02.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Situasi krisis yang sangat jelas!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.05,0:16:06.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau sesederhana ini, orang bodoh\Nsepertiku tak mungkin salah... 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.32,0:16:10.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau bisa, aku mau menghindari\Nsituasi seperti itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.58,0:16:13.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia mengepalkan tinjunya!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.23,0:16:20.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak! Captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.78,0:16:29.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gagal meledak?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana, Eraser?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.35,0:16:43.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku berhasil menghentikan ledakannya,\Ntapi ini cuma sementara.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan berarti bomnya lenyap.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.78,0:16:50.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dia kabur ke belakang menara,\Naku tidak bisa menghapusnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau takkan lolos, Penjahat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, orang itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.91,0:17:03.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Best Jeanist!\NDia berdiri di mana, sih?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.71,0:17:08.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini tim evakuasi udara.\NSemua pihak terkait telah kami hubungi!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.75,0:17:10.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang kami beralih menangani penjahat!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya sudah terhubung...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.44,0:17:14.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benang harapan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Luna Fall!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.51,0:17:38.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini Snipe. Penjahat terbang di atas kubah\Nsudah ditaklukkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.20,0:17:42.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingenium, ini titipan dari Airjet!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.31,0:17:49.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku minta mereka membawa alat komunikasi\Nyang dipakai di Idaten.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadikan tempat ini sebagai pusat komando,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.38,0:17:55.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,bantu pahlawan yang menyebar di berbagai\Nlokasi dan kumpulkan informasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah semuanya, hidupkan mesin kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.25,0:18:01.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Full Throttle.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seni Ninja...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.71,0:18:12.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seribu Jarum!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.11,0:18:14.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeanist!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.90,0:18:15.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeanist!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.85,0:18:22.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Barangnya sudah sampai!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.51,0:18:24.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya datang juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.51,0:18:32.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kabel serat karbon untuk jembatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa tidak masalah?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.45,0:18:35.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benda itu sangat berat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.78,0:18:36.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski beratnya puluhan ton,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.95,0:18:41.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,selama itu terbuat dari serat...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.39,0:18:45.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maka benda itu akan tunduk padaku,\Nsang Fiber Master.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.71,0:18:55.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat! Seperti yang kubilang!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.51,0:18:57.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Para pahlawan datang mengatasi ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.38,0:19:02.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya. Kalau sudah aman...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.75,0:19:03.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koichi,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,ada satu permintaanku padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Apa? Tiba-tiba serius begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong sampaikan pada istri dan bayiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.75,0:19:19.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katakan, ayah kalian\Nadalah pahlawan terbaik.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.59,0:19:23.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah... aku sih, tak keberatan...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.34,0:19:27.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, kami baik-baik saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.05,0:19:28.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu Edgeshot!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.71,0:19:32.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi hal seperti itu... lebih baik\Nkau sampaikan sendiri saat pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.21,0:19:37.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berjuang sampai batas kemampuan
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,atau mengerahkan seluruh kekuatan...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kukira hal-hal seperti itu tak ada\Nhubungannya denganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.25,0:19:47.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi rasanya tak buruk juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.91,0:19:49.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Sayang,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.81,0:19:54.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,rasanya untuk pertama kalinya\Naku bisa dipuji olehmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.65,0:19:59.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana menurutmu?\NApa aku terlihat keren?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.51,0:20:04.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau pikir... aku ini pasangan\Nyang pantas untukmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nak! Apa yang kau lakukan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.91,0:20:14.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Captain! Jangan jatuh, terbanglah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan tolong selamatkan aku juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.31,0:20:19.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jatuh karena kehabisan tenaga\Ndan tak bisa terbang lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar-benar melakukan hal\Nyang tidak perlu!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.55,0:20:23.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu refleks! Tidak sengaja!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuhan! Pahlawan!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa saja! Tolong!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.98,0:20:33.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biarkan aku,\Nsetidaknya selamatkan Koichi...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.41,0:20:36.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setidaknya selamatkan\Nanak pemberani ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.81,0:20:41.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.84,0:20:43.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Captain dan... Crawler?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.97,0:20:48.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka adalah pahlawan tanpa tanda jasa\Ndi pertempuran ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja!\NTakkan kubiarkan mereka mati!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, tidak, tidak...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu takkan terjadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.15,0:20:59.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian memang bertahan cukup lama\Ndi pertarungan putus asa ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.57,0:21:04.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi sejak awal kekuatan serangan\Nsepenuhnya ada di pihak kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.40,0:21:07.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku cuma menahannya\Ndemi eksperimen.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.55,0:21:11.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa mengakhirinya\Nkapan saja kumau.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.17,0:21:17.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia melepaskan diri\Ndengan ledakan bunuh diri?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.61,0:21:23.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat. Dia bersembunyi di balik asap!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.95,0:21:25.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi serius, deh...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.58,0:21:30.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa gerombolan orang lemah ini bertingkah\Nsok keren dan bersemangat?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.78,0:21:33.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyebalkan sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mati saja kalian semua.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.61,0:21:44.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menggandakan tubuh penjahat bom\Ntanpa batas...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.21,0:21:50.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu meledakkannya sekaligus...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.71,0:21:53.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan selesai!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.14,0:23:27.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Krisis besar tanpa jalan keluar!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.71,0:23:30.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan yang datang menyelamatkan\Nadalah pahlawan nomor satu!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.65,0:23:33.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang paling kukagumi,\NAll Might!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.85,0:23:35.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya, "Inilah Pahlawan".
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.91,0:23:39.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di balik layar,\Npertarungan senyap sang guru dimulai.
